# Shwoop HQ

 Come through to the Unleash Space and say "Hi!" to our team. To redeem prizes, or ask question just look out for our volunteers in Shwoop Merch.

![the market banner](https://uoa-bs-maps.s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/The-Market-Logo.png)
# $500 The Market Gift Card

Take 15 seconds to enter your details and go in the draw to win a $500 shopping spree from The Market

[Follow This Link To The Market](https://themarket.com/about/aut-shwoop/?utm_source=aut_shwoop&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=500_dollar_giveaway&fbclid=IwAR1-_eVh9CqwZqrYgmH0coVAt44cCQQ8Iw3SJ01Bo00kgSwQTDxmNoQZrXs)

# Shwoop Facebook

 Message us using our Facebook. Also available in the About page in the menu. [Follow This Link For Our Facebook](https://www.messenger.com/t/shwoopnz)

# More Shwoop?!

We’re continuing next week at The Faculty of Science Buildings all week long! That’s RIGHT - YOU GET EVEN MORE FREE STUFF! We also have a super challenge where the winner gets $1,000 to go towards your Uni Fees for a Science Paper including GenEds.

# Feedback

Hey guys, we’re a tiny little startup and we want to come back next time with a much larger prize pool. It would mean the world if you could please rate us on the store.
